<br>
&quot; Alright your squad is pardoned but I want all of the survivors to meet in my castle for a debriefing. You'll get your time with your families tomorrow , but we need to discuss military matters and such &quot; replied the king commandingly.&quot; ohh also your having a tavern built in your honor , we heard you were especially brave Captain irontoe.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot; Sir It will not be named after me&quot; I stammered<br>
&quot; What , you dare refuse a honor your own king would bestow upon you??? &quot; said the Startled king.<br>
&quot; Yes sir because the honour is not mine to be given to entirely , over 8500 other dwarves died defending this places and they made a much bigger sacrifice than I , lets call the place some with irontoe in it , after the uni... family that fought and died.&quot; I said boldly<br>
<br>
&quot; I like you &quot; said the king.<br>
<br>
After the parade I collapsed , I talked back to the King , the King , If getting in a lot of fights makes you seem weird then battle totally changes you.<br>
<br>
That night dwarves and a few elves met at the council called by king kazon. I recognized a few elves but almost none of the dwarves other than my own squad.<br>
<br>
&quot; First tonite we annouce new weapons &quot; Bellowed the king. &quot; We cannot always ask for the help of our elvish allies so I had a few gnomes create this!&quot;. The thing had a handle and a sort of mini bow placed horizontally on it.<br>
&quot; This is a crossbow , it can punch through most armors easy enough , now imagine at two rows of dwarves armed with these weapons behind a shield big enough to cover their whole body , now imagine a cavalry attack head on and our dwarves don't have pikes. Well they fire and the next row comes up and fires , now either rider or horse is killed or seriously wounded and the charge is broken , any questions???&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot; Next we are going to raise a 12,000 man army to attack the ogres, I know that the elves will give us their help with at least a few thousand bows which will make this force potent. I've also learned that their are mercenary bands of humans with horses that sell their services , we can hire them and then we have the primary three ground attack types.&quot;<br>
<br>
I was quickly getting bored and wanted to train my troops but I figured I probably didn't have any yet.<br>
<br>
we talked long into the night we discussed the ogre stratedgy which was goblin like in that they surprised and overwhlemed , they didn't use much for tactics.We also recieved our awards with much ceremony in front of a three course meal which was torture because I couldn't remember eating since the battle ( was healed during battle and remained unconscious btw ).<br>
<br>
&quot; Wish they'd hurry and give us the damn medal &quot; Somli tried to whisper.<br>
<br>
&quot; Whats was that Captain Somli ? &quot; asked the King<br>
I said &quot; He said He wished the ogres 'd hurry  up and fall on our damn metal , it would've made things easier.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot; Wheres the fun in that &quot; said the king sarcastically ( I think ) ( I swear the King and Trondle are related ).<br>
<br>
